{"tid":2023594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國人對中國好感度上升 對美國看法變差","createTime":"2020-05-19T06:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T10:31:02.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bccf015a9239b1997ed4fea8364e8ed3379ad737","tid":2023594,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:05:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-tw/news/world/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%BD%E6%84%9F%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%8A%E5%B7%AE/ar-BB14gVVg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%2587-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%25B7%25AE%2Far-BB14gVVg&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=364c57c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-tw/news/world/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%BD%E6%84%9F%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%8A%E5%B7%AE/ar-BB14gVVg</a><br />\n<br />\n據法新社報道， 德國科爾伯基金會（ K&ouml;rber-Stiftung）周一（5月18日）在漢堡公布了這份調查結果。調查顯示，在新冠疫情的背景下，甚至有25%的受訪者表示，他們對中國的觀感頗為正面。但與此同時，71%的受訪者也認為，如果在疫情之初中國政府行事更加透明，那麼本可以完全阻止疫情的大爆發或者至少可以讓疫情的規模變小。<br />\n<br />\n另外，雖然依舊有37%的受訪者認為德國首先應該同美國保持緊密關系，但是已有36%的受訪者認為，現在同中國建立緊密關系更為重要。而去年9月在另一份調查中，對同一問題作答的受訪者比例還分別為50%和24%。<br />\n<br />\n科爾伯基金會國際政治研究部主任米勒（ Nora M&uuml;ller ） 表示：&quot;德國人對美國的疑慮不斷增加，這是一個很令人憂心的發展趨勢。大西洋兩端的政治決策者們都應該好好思考。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n不過美國皮尤民調機構所做的一項具有代表性的問卷調查顯示，43%的美國人認為美國應該同德國保持密切關系。這顯示出，美國人仍很重視跨大西洋合作關系。<br />\n<br />\n科爾伯基金會所做的調查中還包含歐盟在疫情中的作為、德國參與解決全球事務、氣候變化等問題。這項調查在4月3日到9日間展開，受訪參與者人數為1000人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />德國男人，等俾中國送去集中營，垃圾"},{"pid":"9342986f1a6d6fc3a26581551f4682d91b4f0505","tid":2023594,"uid":4964,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:06:49.000Z","msg":"建立關係？<br />\n可以呀，等睇抖音話德國妹想嫁中國人做「媳婦」啦"},{"pid":"bf5a74eb86402398d204c12c33703ee7ac478b75","tid":2023594,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9342986f1a6d6fc3a26581551f4682d91b4f0505","tid":2023594,"uid":4964,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:06:49.000Z","msg":"建立關係？<br />\n可以呀，等睇抖音話德國妹想嫁中國人做「媳婦」啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"屌，只有美國人醒覺"},{"pid":"186a78b2e2eece517f532aa3cdd83bd43c07b901","tid":2023594,"uid":250550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:46:54.000Z","msg":"是但啦 <br />\n德咩國 咪又係垃圾歐豬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歐洲一體化嘛"},{"pid":"1c765e5f60786ca3f8c1e7f5a472ecb740f21694","tid":2023594,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:51:37.000Z","msg":"chinazi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66555e0cfebb27c06301df603c00eac9664ba639","tid":2023594,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:52:41.000Z","msg":"NMSL fans"},{"pid":"f29efa726a06e0e24c1dce47515f9b85a912a8dd","tid":2023594,"uid":77416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:53:45.000Z","msg":"新axis power"},{"pid":"782f270e5dbb6163befb69c8435d3242ec1f1ee9","tid":2023594,"uid":121697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"德國科爾伯基金會<br />\n染紅垃圾黎"},{"pid":"37ec2bd57c078469722c789cd9d661dabddefd96","tid":2023594,"uid":77180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:31:02.000Z","msg":"德國已變賤種國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個歐洲越黎越on9"}]}